VIDEO: 27

DRAWING POLYGON WITH TURTLE:
import turtle
t= turtle.Turtle()
t.pencolor("green")
t.color("black")
t.fillcolor("red")
number_side=8
side_length= 100
angle=360.0/number_side

for i in range(number_side):
    t.forward(side_length)
    t.right(angle)
turtle.done()

