SHORTCUT SETTING:
For MAC: Go to IDLE- Preferences- Keys- History Previous- Get new key for selection- Choose your key- press OK
For Windows: Go to Options- configure IDLE- Keys- History Previous-Get new key for selection- Choose your key- press OK

COMMENT AND UNCOMMENT
Convert to comment: Select command and press Alt+3
Convert to uncomment: Select command and press Alt+4

