VIDEO: 40

FOR LOOP

Type 1
for x in range (5):
    print("I am Bolta")

Type 2

y=["hamza", "musab", "solta", "bolta", 10,20]
for x in y:
    print(x)

Type 3
for x in range (5):
    print(x)

Type 4
for x in range (1,5):
    print(x)

Type 5
for x in range (1,20,2):
    print(x)

Type 6
for x in range (20,0, -2):
    print(x)

Type 7 (Combination of for and if, here multiple of 6 is missing in the result)
for x in range (30):
    if x %6!=0:
        print(x)


