VIDEO: 47

USE OF FOR AND ELSE TOGETHER

Only if and else
nums=[3,4,5,7,8,9,3,4]
for num in nums:
    if num%3==0:
        print(num)
    else:
        print("no such number")

Using break function
nums=[3,4,5,7,8,9,3,4]
for num in nums:
    if num%3==0:
        print(num)
        break
    else:
        print("no such number")

